  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 15.65999984741211,
      "text": "A little bit of unnecessary things getting in the way",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 21.81999969482422,
      "text": "Hey, when it's dark, when it's cold, when you need a hand to hold",
      "start": 17.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 26.440000534057617,
      "text": "When you want this and you want to go away, you just need more",
      "start": 21.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 33.040000915527344,
      "text": "Need a little bit of that to get your heart right back on track",
      "start": 26.440000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 39.91999816894531,
      "text": "Yeah, you know that there's only one place you need to go to get that",
      "start": 33.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 48.2599983215332,
      "text": "Anytime you tell me, baby, anytime you need that",
      "start": 41.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 53.619998931884766,
      "text": "You know you got me, Leo, don't you know that you got me",
      "start": 48.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 57.599998474121094,
      "text": "You know you know that you got, that you got me",
      "start": 53.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 62.040000915527344,
      "text": "You know you know, you know that you got me",
      "start": 57.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 64.73999786376953,
      "text": "Always",
      "start": 64.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 69.54000091552734,
      "text": "I don't want to throw, I don't want to throw, I don't want to throw things you got",
      "start": 65.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 73.68000030517578,
      "text": "I don't want to throw, I don't want to throw, I don't want to throw things away",
      "start": 69.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 76.66000366210938,
      "text": "Hey, people are just things we can replace",
      "start": 73.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 82.08000183105469,
      "text": "People are things we can find again",
      "start": 78.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 86.30000305175781,
      "text": "Unique in this world, that's my view on you, baby",
      "start": 82.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 88.44000244140625,
      "text": "Unique is my idea",
      "start": 86.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 93.83999633789062,
      "text": "Even if the title doesn't",
      "start": 90.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 98.12000274658203,
      "text": "Say what you want, it's still there in my mind",
      "start": 93.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 100.76000213623047,
      "text": "Baby, I don't want others",
      "start": 98.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 104.94000244140625,
      "text": "To perceive us in a way",
      "start": 102.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 109.22000122070312,
      "text": "But you light my heart up, baby",
      "start": 106.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 113.86000061035156,
      "text": "And when the dark comes, we'll find a way",
      "start": 109.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 119.31999969482422,
      "text": "Why? Because at the end of the night",
      "start": 114.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 124.5199966430664,
      "text": "I let the pillow in right beside you",
      "start": 119.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 128.9199981689453,
      "text": "Sleep with you to the end of time",
      "start": 124.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 133.4199981689453,
      "text": "Because you got me, baby, you know, and you know",
      "start": 129.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 137.4600067138672,
      "text": "That you got me, baby, you know, you know",
      "start": 133.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 141.44000244140625,
      "text": "That you got me, baby, you know, you know",
      "start": 137.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 147.22000122070312,
      "text": "That you got me always",
      "start": 141.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 151.22000122070312,
      "text": "Baby, you know that you got, that you got me",
      "start": 147.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 155.1199951171875,
      "text": "Baby, you know that you got me",
      "start": 151.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 162.9600067138672,
      "text": "Always and always and all the time",
      "start": 156.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 167.3000030517578,
      "text": "Oh, when the night comes just a little bit",
      "start": 162.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 171.25999450683594,
      "text": "With a fight inside us, we can lose our mind",
      "start": 167.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 175.3800048828125,
      "text": "What doesn't kill us makes us stronger, you'll see",
